#

Lemon Herb Roasted Chicken with Garlic Mashed Potatoes and Seasonal Roasted Vegetables

$25
750 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

dairy

Dietary Tags:

gluten-freeprotein-rich

Tags:

comfort foodfamily mealhearty

Description

A succulent roasted chicken infused with fresh herbs and zesty lemon, complemented by creamy garlic mashed potatoes and a vibrant mix of seasonal vegetables.

Ingredients

  • whole chicken: 4 lbs
  • fresh rosemary: 2 sprigs
  • fresh thyme: 2 sprigs
  • lemon: 1
  • garlic cloves: 4
  • olive oil: 1/4 cup
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • butter: 4 tbsp
  • heavy cream: 1/2 cup
  • russet potatoes: 2 lbs
  • seasonal vegetables (carrots, zucchini, bell peppers): 3 cups
